text: Régis Edouard Klebert Charlet (4 May 1920 - 31 October 1998) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1998 deaths Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chamonix
